data.description: Incredible Rio Communities property on a spacious corner lot is what you've been searching for! Large living room is light and bright thanks to ample windows and skylight and boasts a cozy gas log fireplace. Country kitchen with eat in bar.  Sprawling backyard features backyard access, covered and open patio, trees and grass - perfect for entertaining in the warm months!  Don't let this dream home get away - schedule your showing today!
